        <Paragraph>
           This sample showcases stacked header capability of SfDataGrid. SfDataGrid allows you to have additional unbound header rows, known as stacked header rows that span across GridColumns. You can group two or more columns under each of the stacked header. Stacked header row for the given SfDataGrid is loaded under stacked header rows collection. This collection has definitions for stacked header row that contains stacked columns controlling the behavior and appearance of the stacked header.
